    <p>Crosswater Media is an Oakland-based marketing and media production company that specializes in branding and video production. We believe every company – regardless of size, industry or longevity – has a unique and compelling story to tell. Our recipe for success includes listening, collaborating and strategy. Oh, and fun.</p>
    
