    <p>Tim Haggerty, marketing and branding, has served small businesses, Fortune 500 companies and non-profits across many industries around the world. He is fervent about branding and believes it’s not just the responsibility of giant corporations to be consistent in their communications. Prior to joining Crosswater Media he worked across the marketing spectrum including research, public relations and IMC.</p>
  
